OL,3,CUnite boss joins Birmingham bin worker
OL,4,Crally as strikes pass one year mark
OL,6,FThe leader of Unite is due to join a
OL,7,Frally with striking bin workers in
OL,8,FBirmingham today (Thursday 19 March)
OL,9,Fas their year-long walkout continues.
OL,11,FUnion members started an all-out
OL,12,Fstrike in March last year in a dispute
OL,13,Fover pay, with little or no sign of a
OL,14,Fdeal to end the deadlock.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
