OL,3,CUnite boss joins Birmingham bin worker
OL,4,Crally as strikes pass one year mark
OL,6,FGeneral secretary Sharon Graham will
OL,7,Frenew Unite's support for the strikers
OL,8,Fduring the rally on Thursday, which
OL,9,Ffollows the announcement of a fine
OL,10,Fagainst the union of #265,000, with
OL,11,F#170,000 costs, after the council took
OL,12,Flegal action over picketing.
OL,14,FMs Graham said: "Our members taking
OL,15,Findustrial action have Unite's
OL,16,Funwavering support.
OL,26,@vD@QOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
