OL,3,CUnite boss joins Birmingham bin worker
OL,4,Crally as strikes pass one year mark
OL,6,FMajid Mahmood, the council's cabinet
OL,7,Fmember for environment and transport,
OL,8,Fsaid after the fine was announced: "We
OL,9,Fare pleased the judge has accepted the
OL,10,Fevidence that members of Unite
OL,11,Frepeatedly breached the injunction
OL,12,Fordered by the court earlier this year.
OL,14,F"We are working to keep the city safe
OL,15,Fand clean and thanks to the injunction
OL,16,Fhave maintained a weekly collection
OL,17,Ffor Birmingham families.
OL,26,@pD@dOUvD@AOU
